&lt;p&gt;This problem is similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-13990&quot; title=&quot;Update features will fail in KRaft mode&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-13990&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-13990&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I already found this problem, I also found it only occur in the kraft controllers and the brokers are not infected by this, so this problem doesn&apos;t have any impact currently since the finalizedFeatures is not used in kraft controller.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
